<p>W3C owns and manages the <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG22/">Web Content Accessibility Guidelines</a> (known as WCAG).
</p>
<p>WCAG 2.2 was published in October 2023. You should comply now to make sure products and services are ready by October 2024. See <a href="https://www.gov.uk/service-manual/helping-people-to-use-your-service/understanding-wcag">guidance on understanding WCAG 2.2 in the GOV.UK service manual</a>.</p>

